line_1: While the sleek tygers roll and bask,
line_2: Of beasts — the beaver plods his task;

line_1: To Gipsies brown in Summer-Glades who bask.
line_2: An useless were, and eke an endless Task:

line_1: To Gipsies brown in Summer-Glades who bask.
line_2: Yea many a Man perdie I could unmask,

line_1: To Gipsies brown in Summer-Glades who bask.
line_2: With Tape-ty'd Trash, and Suits of Fools that ask
